{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"5c43096952","title":"关于大批判的谈话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"67ae38b9c4","index":0,"year":1967,"month":5,"day":2,"articleId":"5c43096952"}],"tags":[{"id":"07ed767d50","name":"大批判","type":"主题"},{"id":"314ad57c4d","name":"对话","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"c20d333791","name":"关键人物文稿","type":"文稿大类"},{"id":"e2305b9e63","name":"毛泽东","type":"主题"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库(第一版)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"6bb7622be0","type":"title","text":"关于大批判的谈话","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5c43096952"},{"id":"d459bdc5cd","type":"paragraph","text":"关于大批判的谈话","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5c43096952"},{"id":"c493773203","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5c43096952"},{"id":"95d7fc2353","type":"paragraph","text":"1967.05.02","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5c43096952"},{"id":"39fa772624","type":"paragraph","text":"大批判要慎重，要确实，要调查清楚。调查清楚，批判才有力量，否则就会一风吹。引他（指刘少奇）的话不能只顾头不顾尾。批判要站得住。","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5c43096952"},{"id":"054a54d7a5","type":"paragraph","text":"“托拉斯”这个名词，不能一概驳，主要驳他走资本主义道路。有些旧名词要赋予新的意义。","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5c43096952"},{"id":"e7edb669c5","type":"paragraph","text":"“驯服工具论”要批判，但也要有无产阶级纪律。服从、团结，那是有条件的。","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5c43096952"},{"id":"0bd8ba34e9","type":"paragraph","text":"今年形势好，布、粮还是要抓。社论要搞快一些。","index":7,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5c43096952"},{"id":"cd26264662","type":"paragraph","text":"批判文章文字要短。一、二千字，写一个问题，一个问题说明了就行，不能超过三千字。长了没有人看，看了也记不清。","index":8,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5c43096952"},{"id":"e65a25dd7f","type":"paragraph","text":"彭、罗、陆、杨可以称为“反革命修正主义分子”，其他人称“修正主义分子”。“中国的赫鲁晓夫”，文章中提，在标题上不要提。","index":9,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5c43096952"}],"page":{"id":"53bf88510d","publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5c43096952","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}